dcterms:description: The Portland cement dataset contains characteristics of 13 cement mixtures, where the y-outcome variable is heat (cals/gm) evolved during hardening. The dataset includes 4 predictor variables that represent ingredient percentages, which appear to have been rounded down to full integers.
dcterms:title: Portland cement dataset
